Execute 'make' to obtain the executable file 'andromeda'
  - make with parameters:
    - bls:    block size in CUDA code (default 256)
    - score:  initial conditions using host functions (default using device)
              This parameter can be set to any value
  - Example: make andromeda bls=16 score=1
  - Use 'make clean' to delete the executable file
  - target:
     - default :  create exectuable file simulating Antennae
     - antennae:  as above
     - andromeda: create exectuable file simulating Andromeda Galaxy collision
     - all:       create both antennae and andromeda
     - clean:     remove all executable files generated by this Makefile
     - Example: make antennae
